"title": "5895: intimacy",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5895",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Close relationships are part of God's will for human life. Scripture speaks of intimate relationships between Jesus Christ and the Father, between God and his people, and between various individuals.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's intimate relationship with his Father</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:27\">MAT 11:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:17\">MAT 3:17</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:11\">MRK 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:22\">LUK 3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:20\">JHN 5:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:30\">JHN 10:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:38\">JHN 10:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:10-John14:11\">JHN 14:10–14:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:21\">JHN 17:21</a></p>\n<h2>God's intimate relationship with his people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:3\">JHN 17:3</a></strong> <em>“know” speaks of close personal relationship rather than theoretical or academic knowledge.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:15-2Chr7:16\">2CH 7:15–7:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps148:14\">PSA 148:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:6\">HOS 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:21\">JHN 14:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:4\">JHN 15:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:15\">JHN 15:15</a></p>\n<h2>Images of God's desire for intimacy with his people</h2>\n<h3>God as a father</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:9\">JER 31:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:13\">PSA 103:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:20\">JER 31:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:1-Hos11:4\">HOS 11:1–11:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:15\">ROM 8:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:1\">1JN 3:1</a></p>\n<h3>God as a husband</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:5\">ISA 62:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:4-Isa54:8\">ISA 54:4–54:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:14\">JER 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:19\">HOS 2:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25-Eph5:27\">EPH 5:25–5:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:7\">REV 19:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:2\">REV 21:2</a></p>\n<h2>Intimate relationships between men and women</h2>\n<h3>As God's good purpose</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:18\">GEN 2:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:27-Gen1:28\">GEN 1:27–1:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:24\">GEN 2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:5\">MAT 19:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:7\">MRK 10:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:16\">1CO 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:28\">EPH 5:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:31\">EPH 5:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:3-1Tim4:4\">1TI 4:3–4:4</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of such close relationships</h3>\n<p>Jacob and Rachel:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:20\">GEN 29:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:30\">GEN 29:30</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth4:13\">RUT 4:13</a> <em>Boaz and Ruth</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:5\">1SA 1:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:8\">1SA 1:8</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:17\">EST 2:17</a> <em>Xerxes and Esther</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:15-Song1:16\">SNG 1:15–1:16</a> <em>Solomon and his beloved</em></p>\n<h2>Intimacy in other relationships</h2>\n<h3>Close friendships commended</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:24\">PRO 18:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:17\">PRO 17:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:10\">PRO 27:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:9-Eccl4:12\">ECC 4:9–4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:13\">JHN 15:13</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of close friendships</h3>\n<p>David and Jonathan:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:1\">1SA 18:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:3\">1SA 18:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:2\">2KI 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:4\">2KI 2:4</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:16\">2TI 1:16</a> <em>Paul and Onesiphorus</em></p>\n<h2>Examples of intimate family relationships</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:3\">GEN 37:3</a> <em>Jacob and his son Joseph</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:16\">RUT 1:16</a> <em>Ruth and her mother-in-law Naomi</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:33\">2SA 18:33</a> <em>David and his son Absalom</em></p>",
